            "title": "Customers Bank appoints Stephen Wyremski as COO",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Customers Bank, a subsidiary of Customers Bancorp (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CUBI\" title=\"Customers Bancorp, Inc.\">CUBI</a></span>) on Monday announced the appointment of <span class=\"person\">Steve Wyremski</span> as Chief Operating Officer, effective January 26, 2026.</li>\n<li>Wyremski joined Customers Bank in 2024 as a strategic advisor. Prior to joining Customers Bank, Wyremski served as CFO of a <span class=\"location\">New York</span>-based commercial bank with over $100 billion in assets. </li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20376418-customers-bank-appoints-stephen-wyremski-as-chief-operating-officer\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
